{"tid":1534761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[白色恐怖迫你跪］罷工日Zara香港閉店 共青團批亂港","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:20.000Z","uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa19ff23d9168a0b689f76130d623db7f7f90bfa","tid":1534761,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"國際連鎖時裝品牌Zara昨日有香港分店暫停營業，被內地傳媒質疑是響應罷工，官方《環球時報》稱Zara需要做出鄭重說明並糾正做法，強調內地公眾不會接受Zara門店在香港的表現。<br />\n<br />\nZara今日在官方微博發表聲明，稱公司擁護中華人民共和國領土主權完整，一貫支持「一國兩制」。聲明又說，Zara從未支持罷工，亦未有發布任何相關言論或進行相關行為。<br />\n<br />\nZara今日在官微否認罷工 支持「一國兩制」<br />\n<br />\n有香港網民就反對《逃犯條例》修訂發起罷工，呼籲各個行業於9月2日及3日進行「三罷」， 即罷工、罷市、罷課。<br />\n<br />\nZara位於銅鑼灣的分店昨日貼出告示，暫停營業一天，未有解釋原因。九龍區海港城分店據稱亦暫停營業，而港島區太古城及新界區分店則照常開舖。<br />\n<br />\n共青團在官方微博「共青團中央」指出Zara疑似聲援「亂港分子」，並貼出「勿作幫兇」圖片。《環球時報》昨晚深夜則發出社評，質疑Zara在「這樣的敏感時刻」關店的動機。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣海港城店停業 太古城及新界店開門<br />\n<br />\n社評又稱，人們不能不做出這樣的分析：Zara香港公司、至少它的一些門店的管理層有呼應「三罷」的主觀意願，甚至他們也願意用相關的表現出一出特殊的風頭，他們大概認為因此而承擔一些品牌的風險是值得的。<br />\n<br />\nZara去年曾因將港澳台標註成「國家」而在中國內地網民中引起強烈不滿，今次人們很容易對這兩件事產生聯想。而且如果說上一次的事情有屬於「疏漏」可能的話，星期一Zara部分港店關門則只能被看成是故意為之。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報：Zara表現與止暴制亂不同方向<br />\n<br />\n社評最後說，Zara需要做出鄭重說明並且糾正自己的做法，給香港愛國愛港的市民和內地廣大公眾一個嚴肅的交代。如今香港的事情聚集了中國全社會的大量注意力，公眾不會接受Zara門店在香港的表現。 Zara不應做出嚴重的誤判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2443066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2443066&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=0d68084c\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2443066</a>"},{"pid":"c6365bdc498e343c31b18619360c832c8206285f","tid":1534761,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5e03e21d787c56920530724421708ffad42ee4a","tid":1534761,"uid":249885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"人地做唔做生意關你閪事"},{"pid":"f0a6c744d84cdd2d03766374cd977b0ac19a1535","tid":1534761,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"e36470f3d35f54b1c33fc14087bf0470ee0bd457","tid":1534761,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"已經有國泰 大班 周柏豪 被中共迫跪了"},{"pid":"8c562ed58b2487da602e155902a4d59837ba9939","tid":1534761,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d0f58273c2d4f693de99e95c4cdfb3115ef303","tid":1534761,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://e.blog.xuite.net/e/6/4/8/10166094/blog_972035/txt/147455116/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fe.blog.xuite.net%2Fe%2F6%2F4%2F8%2F10166094%2Fblog_972035%2Ftxt%2F147455116%2F0.jpg&h=204164ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a3ddcfe34c4d893fbcc5a6e7d5975d43120723b","tid":1534761,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}